KERNEL: TRIPLE_PULSE_MOUNTAIN
AUTHOR: David Wise / GPT-5.5 Thinking
MODE: safe simulation, linear core array

LAW:
  PULSE x3 DOWN THE MOUNTAIN
  END AT 27
  27 = 0 = 27

STATES:
  0..26  : descent / accumulation gates
  27     : terminal wall / coherence gate
  0      : zero well / compression singularity
  27     : reconstituted exit state

CHANNELS:
  RED   : leading heat/intensity channel
  GOLD  : witness/phase channel
  BLUE  : return/cooling channel

EXECUTION:
  FIRE_X3()
  FOR gate 0..27:
    advance all three pulses along fixed centerline
    clamp pulse to tunnel boundary
    accumulate compression = (gate/27)^2
  IF gate == 27:
    collapse all channels to zero well
    discharge as shock ring
    reconstitute as 27 in phase N+1
  RESET_DRIFT()
  REPEAT()

SAFETY:
  simulator only
  no physical laser build parameters
  no power, focusing, burning, or real-world cutting guidance
